summary: The long-awaited animated prequel to the popular Transformers film franchise, "Transformers One," has unveiled its first trailer, providing a glimpse into the origins of the iconic characters Optimus Prime and Megatron. The trailer reveals a younger, more relatable version of the Autobot and Decepticon leaders, as they navigate the challenges of adolescence and the impending conflict that will shape their destinies. Chris Hemsworth lends his voice to Optimus Prime, while Scarlett Johansson and Brian Tyree Henry voice other prominent roles. The film, set on the planet Cybertron, explores the origins of the Transformers and their connection to Earth, promising an expansive and visually stunning animated adventure. The trailer showcases the advanced technology and imaginative world-building that fans have come to expect from the Transformers franchise.

The game enters Early Access this week on PC, with a $39.99 price tag. Reviews and walkthroughs are already available, providing insights into the game's story, characters, and mechanics. Despite being playable on Steam Deck, the recommended PC specifications may be demanding. The game showcases a significant graphical evolution from Moon Studios' previous work, "Ori and the Blind Forest," while also supporting keyboard and mouse controls. These articles highlight the anticipation and excitement surrounding "No Rest For The Wicked" as it prepares to make its Early Access debut.

name: Fire ants
summary: Fire ants, an invasive species in Australia, have prompted concerns and calls for action. A Senate inquiry has emphasized the need for improved cooperation and transparency in eradication efforts, while new research estimates potential costs of up to $22 billion by 2040. Discoveries of fire ants in Oakey and concerns about slow government response have heightened urgency. Experts warn of the threat posed by these pests, calling for an all-out war to prevent further spread and severe consequences. Farmers in New South Wales demand funding increases to combat the menace, while The Weekly Times reports the detection of red fire ants amid funding review calls. Sky News Australia highlights fears of an outbreak and the need for increased funding. An Australian town is on alert due to the presence of fire ants, known for their painful stings. Landscape Management magazine advises caution during spring to avoid encounters with these invasive pests.

Bayern Munich knocked Arsenal out of the Champions League, while Manchester City and Arsenal both exited the competition.
